<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='94937' id='t-94937'>Until one day she came back to my office</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='96881' id='t-96881'>and she was bawling, she was just crying.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='99300' id='t-99300'>She had been on scene at a long line,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='101926' id='t-101926'>where the woman running the line
