<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='108887' id='t-108887'>There's too many people!&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='110807' id='t-110807'>And this man with diabetes
doesn't get food in time,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='114386' id='t-114386'>his blood sugar drops too low,
and he collapses into a coma.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='118695' id='t-118695'>As soon as I heard that audio,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='120251' id='t-120251'>I knew that this would be
