<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='123520' id='t-123520'>that could really describe
what was going on at food banks.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:18
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='127290' id='t-127290'>So here's the real line.
