</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='162340' id='t-162340'>Voice: OK, he's having a seizure.</span>
