<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='203084' id='t-203084'>He's very cautious not to step on this guy</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='205118' id='t-205118'>who isn't really there, right?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:38
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='207506' id='t-207506'>So that piece ended up
going to Sundance in 2012,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='210633' id='t-210633'>a kind of amazing thing,
and it was the first virtual reality film</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='214578' id='t-214578'>ever, basically.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='217062' id='t-217062'>And when we went, I was really terrified.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='219047' id='t-219047'>I didn't really know
how people were going to react</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='221508' id='t-221508'>and what was going to happen.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='222921' id='t-222921'>And we showed up
