</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:56
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='225842' id='t-225842'>(Video) Oh, you're crying.
You're crying. Gina, you're crying.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:00
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='229851' id='t-229851'>So you can hear
the surprise in my voice, right?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='232595' id='t-232595'>And this kind of reaction ended up being
the kind of reaction we saw</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='236214' id='t-236214'>over and over and over:</span>
