<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='256999' id='t-256999'>So after this piece was made,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='260198' id='t-260198'>the dean of the cinema school at USC,
