<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='287966' id='t-287966'>as that's where ISIS is really operating.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='290458' id='t-290458'>And then we also recreated a street scene</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='293188' id='t-293188'>in which a young girl is singing
